		<descriptionSet>
			<description source=" " lang="en" script="latn">On this lobby card for the Hindi movie "Satyam Shivam Sundaram", released in 1978, the left section has a movie still of the two leading actors, Shashi Kapoor (Ranjeet) and Zeenat Aman (Rupa). Zeenat Aman is dancing in a shallow river wearing wet clothes as Shashi Kapoor looks towards her. Shashi Kapoor is also completely wet and is wearing a pair of shorts. In the background a tree on the banks of the river can be seen.
To the right of the image, under the emblem of Raj Kapoor Films, Zeenat Aman is shown again, wearing a revealing blouse and a tight, short dhoti wrapped in the style of a langot (cloth wrapped so it goes between the legs).</description>
		</descriptionSet>
